e.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/sydney-sweeney-don-arnold-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/sydney-sweeney-don-arnold-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/sydney-sweeney-don-arnold-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3562265" class="wp-caption-text">悉尼·斯威尼.图片来源：唐·阿诺德/盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>第三季的任务尤为艰巨，在三年的拍摄间隙中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/euphoria-actor-angus-cloud-has-died-aged-25-3475909">，扮演菲斯的演员安格斯·克劳德于去年八月初因意外服药过量去世</a>。</p><p>新一季将于 2025 年初开始制作，这意味着该剧最早可能会在 2025 年底首播，不过 2026 年上映的可能性似乎更大。赞达亚在四月份表示，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/zendaya-weighs-in-on-euphoria-delay-its-beyond-me-3619076">该剧的延误“超出了我的承受能力”</a> ，而斯威尼则告诉<em>《NME》</em> ，虽然在制作<em>《幸福感》</em>时“当我回到家时就像回到家一样”， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/sydney-sweeney-immaculate-euphoria-madame-web-snl-3603533">但她“不知道我多久才能回家”</a> 。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/euphoria-season-2-review-zendaya-hbo-3132916">在<em>《NME</em> 》对<em>《欣快感》</em>第二季的五星级评论中</a>，瑞安·达利写道，它“以某种方式进一步加剧了痛苦，使几乎所有主要参与者都更深地陷入了痛苦之网”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3604716" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3604716" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3604716" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Euphoria_Sydney_Sweeney.jpg" alt="欣快感" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Euphoria_Sydney_Sweeney.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Euphoria_Sydney_Sweeney-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Euphoria_Sydney_Sweeney-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Euphoria_Sydney_Sweeney-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Euphoria_Sydney_Sweeney-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Euphoria_Sydney_Sweeney-106